sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Playwright (Test)
    participant F as Frontend (Next.js)
    participant B as Backend (NestJS)
    participant DB as Database (Prisma)
    participant SMS as SmsService (SNS)

    Note over P, SMS: Standard Flow (TEST_MODE=false)
    P->>F: Input Phone Number
    F->>B: POST /auth/login
    B->>B: Generate Random OTP
    B->>DB: Save OTP Hash
    B->>SMS: sendOtp(phone, otp)
    SMS-->>B: Success
    B-->>F: OK
    P->>F: Input OTP (from SMS/Logs)
    F->>B: POST /auth/verify
    B->>DB: Verify OTP
    B-->>F: JWT Token
    F-->>P: Redirect to Dashboard

    Note over P, SMS: Test Flow (TEST_MODE=true)
    P->>F: Input Phone Number
    F->>B: POST /auth/login
    B->>B: Use E2E_FIXED_OTP (123456)
    B->>DB: Save OTP Hash
    B-->>F: OK (Skip SMS)
    P->>F: Input "123456"
    F->>B: POST /auth/verify
    B->>DB: Verify OTP
    B-->>F: JWT Token
    F-->>P: Redirect to Dashboard
